# Local overrides for the Electric Agents mobile app. Copy to `.env`
# (which is gitignored) when you need them; production builds use the
# defaults baked into the source.

# Override the Electric Cloud dashboard the OAuth sign-in flow targets.
# Defaults to https://dashboard.electric-sql.cloud (see
# `src/lib/cloudAuth.ts` -> `PROD_DASHBOARD_URL`). Point this at a PR
# deployment (e.g. https://dashboard-pr-1504.electric-sql.dev) while
# testing admin-API changes before they reach production.
#
# Note: `EXPO_PUBLIC_*` vars are inlined into the JS bundle at build
# time by Metro, so every commit / build picks up whatever value is
# set when bundling. Keep this file local and never commit a `.env`.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_ELECTRIC_DASHBOARD_URL=https://dashboard.electric-sql.cloud
